high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward to the counter left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the right to face the counter.
Use the butter knife to cut the potato into slices.
Put the butter knife down on the right side of the counter.
Pick up a slice of the potato.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go forward to the microwave that is above the sink.
Put the potato in in the microwave and turn it on to cook, then remove the cooked potato and close the door.
Turn around, turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right to the counter where the coffee maker is.
Put the potato on the counter in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked potato on a counter.
